   <!-- 4. Tech Stack (for React + Bootstrap 5)  -->


   | Part              | Technology                      |
| ----------------- | ------------------------------- |
| **Frontend**      | React.js + Bootstrap 5 + CSS    |
| **Backend**       | Node.js + Express (optional)    |
| **Database**      | MongoDB / MySQL (optional)      |
| **Hosting**       | Netlify / Vercel / AWS / Render |
| **Icons & Fonts** | Font Awesome, Google Fonts      |



Development Roadmap 

| Phase       | Task                     | Description                                               |
| ----------- | ------------------------ | --------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Day 1-2** | Project Setup            | Create React app, install Bootstrap, setup file structure |
| **Day 3-4** | Navbar + Home Page       | Hero section, basic layout                                |
| **Day 5-6** | Menu Page                | Create food card components with props                    |
| **Day 7**   | About + Contact Pages    | Static information + contact form                         |
| **Day 8**   | Reservation Page         | Create reservation form                                   |
| **Day 9**   | Styling & Responsiveness | Add Bootstrap classes and CSS                             |
| **Day 10**  | Testing & Deployment     | Host website on Netlify or Vercel                         |


